{"tid":960821,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"水行俠=集百家大成","createTime":"2018-12-29T16:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T10:53:23.000Z","uid":65354,"like":13,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6f5d95f11dfc5e4f701eec9febff377fd9e8d2","tid":960821,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:51:02.000Z","msg":"Percy Jackson元素 - Half-blood 海神, 手持Trident可以喺海洋屈機<br />\n<br />\nMCU元素:<br />\nCaptain America - 刀槍不入,神力<br />\n<br />\n黑豹 - 高科技+隱秘國度, 決戰搶皇位,輸左唔服氣之後再抽過<br />\n<br />\n雷神 - 只有王者先可以拎起支Trident 仲要兩把野鑄造嘅方法都有啲似<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIron man - Blant Manta改左件ironman甲出嚟同aquaman打<br />\n<br />\n鷹眼 - 女主個老豆King Nereus, 步百穿揚 但武器係Atlantis嘅步槍<br />\n<br />\n喺船打The Trench一大堆怪=Avengers New York打Chitauri + Jurassic Park (仲有一堆恐龍, 世界觀同Journey to the centre of the Earch一樣) <br />\n<br />\n成套戲一路睇一路就諗起其他唔同戲<br />\n<br />\n套戲嘅劇情其實算一般 但值得一讚係打鬥場面,配樂,特技都係top notch <br />\n<br />\n以一套英雄片嚟講, 其實已經做得唔錯 因為英雄片最緊要係角色塑造, 而Aquaman嘅性格同心路歷程其實喺套戲係好出<br />\n<br />\n麻煩巴打幫我頂一頂啲DC手足 我走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4888c1170b1c9a664560c3f96993a162f0f2eb8a","tid":960821,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:52:01.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"e3e81499a1a37353bfb44b87efb48b53cc4dc992","tid":960821,"uid":1330,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:53:55.000Z","msg":"入海溝個畫面靚撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5daf6f5c76c41a67cc94f09513d6277f0e9ca183","tid":960821,"uid":188282,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"西西里島-達文西密碼"},{"pid":"1ad8a77d3bf5c7bd12003439cf801a88469ee83b","tid":960821,"uid":105605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5daf6f5c76c41a67cc94f09513d6277f0